1. *Vašom* odlukom smo otkazali sastanak. (By your decision, we canceled the meeting.)
2. Nadam se da ste zadovoljni *vašim* novim poslom. (I hope you're satisfied with your new job.)
3. Kada budete spremni, molim vas da mi pošaljete *vašu* prijavu. (When you're ready, please send me your application.)
4. *Vašom* podrškom smo uspeli da ostvarimo naš cilj. (With your support, we managed to achieve our goal.)
5. Molim vas da mi kažete šta mislite o *vašim* predlozima. (Please tell me what you think about your proposals.)
6. Ova knjiga je napisana *vašim* jezikom. (This book is written in your language.)
7. Da li ste zadovoljni *vašom* platom? (Are you satisfied with your salary?)
8. Hvala vam na *vašem* vremenu i trudu. (Thank you for your time and effort.)
9. Ovo je *vaša* prilika da pokažete svoje znanje. (This is your opportunity to show your knowledge.)
10. Molim vas da ne pravite nikakve izmene u *vašem* izveštaju. (Please do not make any changes to your report.)